snippet.title: FANTASTIC BEAST 3 FAILS: AMBER HEARD WINS AGAIN - Warner Brothers BANS Johnny Depp | The Gossipy
snippet.description:
FANTASTIC BEAST 3 FAILS: AMBER HEARD WINS AGAIN - Warner Brothers BANS Johnny Depp | The Gossipy

In this video, Celebrity Craze shows J.K Rowling's Reaction to Losing Johnny Depp in the upcoming Fantastic Beasts And Where To Find Them Movie. As you know, Johnny has been replaced by Mads Mikkelsen and according to J.K. Rowling, this can literally destroy the movie series!

With the initial court date being pushed back, Johnny Depp and Amber Heard have been given some more time in order to gather more evidence for their individual cases. For quite some time, the two were firing evidence at each other in order to win in court. 

Ever since the recent release of the footage of the LAPD officers from the penthouse night of Amber Heard and Johnny Depp, things have not been looking all too bright for Amber Heard. Her team has been working tirelessly in order to back up her side, however Johnny Depp seems to have made the attempt to strike back.

Now she is chilling and taking photos on set of the new Aquaman 2 movie. Set to hit theaters in 2022. This is enraging a lot of Johnny Depp supporters.

#JKRowling #JohnnyDepp #FantasticBeasts #MadsMikkelsen #AmberHeard #JusticeForJohnny #Aquaman 2 #FilmStreak
